The '''Fiji '''[Amateur]''' Cycling Association''' or '''FACA''' is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Fiji]].

The FACA is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Oceanian Cycling Confederation|OCC]].

==External links==
* [http://www.sportingpulse.com/assoc_page.cgi?c=2-1375-0-0-0 Fiji Cycling Association official website]

The Fiji Cycling Association is now known as [http://fjcycling.com Cycling Fiji]

