{{Infobox national volleyball team |name=Serbia U18 |gender=women | type = U18 |image=Serbia volleyball team.png |website=[http://www.ossrb.org Official website] |federation=Serbian Volleyball Federation |confederation=CEV |coach= |pattern_la1=|pattern_b1=|pattern_ra1=|leftarm1=0000FF|body1=0000FF|rightarm1=0000FF|shorts1=0000FF |pattern_la2=|pattern_b2=|pattern_ra2=|leftarm2=FF0000|body2=ffffff|rightarm2=FF0000|shorts2=0000FF |Olympic apps= None |Olympic first = |Olympic best = |World Champs apps = 6 |World Champs first = 2007 |World Champs best = {{World2}} ''Silver'' : ([[2009 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship|2009]]) |Regional name = |Regional apps = |Regional first = |Regional best = |}} The '''Serbia women's national under-18 volleyball team''' represents [[Serbia]] in international [[women]]'s [[volleyball]] [[competitions]] and friendly matches under the age 18 and it is ruled by the [[Serbian Volleyball Federation]] That is an affiliate of [[Federation Internationale de Volleyball|Federation of International Volleyball]] '''FIVB''' and also a part of [[European Volleyball Confederation]] '''CEV'''.
