'''8 May 1945 Stadium''' ({{Lang-ar|ملعب 8 ماي 1945}}) is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Sétif]], Algeria. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[ES Sétif]]. The stadium holds 25,000 people.

