{{Unreferenced|date=February 2007}}
The '''Super Coupe [[Roger Milla]]''' is a match competition in [[Cameroon]] [[football (soccer)|football]], played between the [[Cameroon Premiere Division]] champions and the [[Cameroon Cup]] winners.

==Finals==
*1999 : '''[[Sable FC]]''' (Batié) 1-0 [[Canon Yaoundé]] (Yaoundé)
*2000 : '''[[Kumbo Strikers FC]]''' (Kumbo) 1-0 [[Fovu Baham|Fovu Club]]   (Baham)
*2001 : '''[[Fovu Baham|Fovu Club]]''' (Baham)  1-0 [[Coton Sport FC de Garoua|Coton Sport FC]]  (Garoua)
*2002 : '''[[Mount Cameroon FC]]''' (Buéa) 2-0 [[Canon Yaoundé]] (Yaoundé)

NB: in 2003 and 2004 [[Coton Sport FC de Garoua|Coton Sport FC]] won the league-and-cup double and apparently no Super Cup match was organised.

