'''Við Djúpumýrar''' is a multi-use stadium in [[Klaksvík]], [[Faroe Islands]]. It is mostly used mostly for football matches. Við Djúpumýrar is the home ground of [[KÍ Klaksvík]] and has a capacity of 530 seats.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.soccerandequipment.com/may-2010-roundup.html | title=Cup final moved again – date and venue! | publisher=soccerandequipment.com | date=28 May 2010 | accessdate=9 November 2015}}</ref>

